highlights.text: The Weeknd has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Sacrifice” is the highest at #3.
“Love Grows (Where My Rosemary Goes)” by Edison Lighthouse is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 50 spots at #115.
“Sacrifice” by The Weeknd is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #3.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 258 weeks straight.
